  "comment_text": {
    "snp5.13:4.3": "Read (with Niddesa) as accusative plural. Norman reads <i lang='pi' translate='no'>ādānasatte</i> as locative singular, but compare the similar construction at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/thag19.1/en/sujato#20.3'>Thag 19.1:20.3</a>, where the former part of the line is accusative. "
